Crypt-X509 version 0.01
=======================

Crypt::X509 is an object oriented X.509 certificate parser with numerous
methods for directly extracting information from certificates.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires:

  Convert::ASN1

COPYRIGHT AND LICENCE

This module is based in part on the x509decode script, which was
contributed to Convert::ASN1 in 2002 by Norbert Klasen.

